452
00:23:04,872 --> 00:23:08,572
Tidak. Lagipula, dia bertindak bodoh.

453
00:23:08,572 --> 00:23:11,938
Namun sekarang kau berada di sisinya,

454
00:23:11,938 --> 00:23:13,272
